#### ❓ What lifecycle method is equivalent to `useEffect(() => {}, [])`?

- [ ] A. `componentDidUpdate`
- [ ] B. `componentWillUnmount`
- [ ] C. `componentDidMount`
- [ ] D. `shouldComponentUpdate`

<details>
<summary>✅ Answer</summary>

**C. `componentDidMount`**

Both run once after the first render.

