#### ❓ What is the Context API best suited for?

- [ ] A. High-frequency updates like mouse position
- [ ] B. Low-frequency global data like theme, locale, or authentication
- [ ] C. Replacing all prop passing
- [ ] D. Server-side state

<details>
<summary>✅ Answer</summary>

**B. Low-frequency global data like theme, locale, or authentication**

Every consumer re-renders when context changes, making it unsuitable for rapidly-changing values without additional memoization strategies.

</details>

