#### ❓ What does `Partial<T>` do?

- [ ] A. Makes all properties required
- [ ] B. Makes all properties optional
- [ ] C. Removes properties
- [ ] D. Converts types to strings

<details>
<summary>✅ Answer</summary>

**B. Makes all properties optional**

