#### ❓ What does `Required<T>` do?

- [ ] A. Makes all properties optional
- [ ] B. Makes all properties required, removing `?`
- [ ] C. Picks specific properties
- [ ] D. Creates readonly properties

<details>
<summary>✅ Answer</summary>

**B. Makes all properties required, removing `?`**

The opposite of `Partial<T>`.

</details>

